algorithms.imageProcessing

Class CurvatureScaleSpaceInflectionEdgeMapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • algorithms.imageProcessing.AbstractCurvatureScaleSpaceInflectionMapper
      • algorithms.imageProcessing.CurvatureScaleSpaceInflectionEdgeMapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICurvatureScaleSpaceInflectionMapper

    public final class CurvatureScaleSpaceInflectionEdgeMapper
extends AbstractCurvatureScaleSpaceInflectionMapper
    class to map contours from edges from one image to another and return the matched inflection points and a transformation matrix that can be applied to the first to put it into the frame of the second. The algorithm used for matching scale space image contours is documented in CSSContourMatcherWrapper
    Author:
    nichole
    See Also:
    CSSContourMatcherWrapper
